des: Learn to have Conscious, Loving & Respectful Relationships! This educational podcast is for Successful Women who Struggle in Love; yet much applies to men and couples too. Overcome Pain, a Negative Mindset, Fears & Anxiety, Lack of Trust, Codependency & Emotional Triggers due to past Childhood or Relationship Trauma - to Have the Life You Desire & The Love You Deserve! I'm Coach Riana Milne, a Certified, Global Life & Love Coach & Cert. Clinical Trauma Professional. I’m a #1 Bestselling Author and taught Personal Life Transformation for over 38 years to teens and adults of all ages. This 30 minute to1-hr podcast is posted on Fridays.
